      • handleReply

        public void handleReply(MintMessage msg,
               MintMessage rply)
        Description copied from interface: MintReply
        Callback to accept a reply. This method is invoked when a non-null reply is sent for a message. It is passed the original message object and a MintMessage object representing the reply. Note that the reply object can be null if no reply was returned.
